---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-comparison', text: 'Coverage Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'pricing', text: 'Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'network-and-claims', text: 'Network and Claims', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-should-choose', text: 'Who Should Choose Which', level: 2 },
  { id: 'verdict', text: 'Our Verdict', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'GeoBlue Review', href: '/providers/geoblue' },
  { title: 'AXA Global Review', href: '/providers/axa-global' },
  { title: 'Best Expat Insurance', href: '/best/expat-health-insurance' },
];

const coverageColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'geoblue', header: 'GeoBlue' },
  { key: 'axa', header: 'AXA Global' },
];

const coverageRows = [
  { feature: 'Inpatient Care', geoblue: true, axa: true },
  { feature: 'Outpatient Care', geoblue: true, axa: true },
  { feature: 'Mental Health', geoblue: 'Moderate', axa: 'Limited' },
  { feature: 'Maternity', geoblue: '12 mo wait', axa: '10-12 mo wait' },
  { feature: 'Dental', geoblue: 'Optional', axa: 'Optional' },
  { feature: 'Telemedicine', geoblue: true, axa: true },
  { feature: 'Medical Evacuation', geoblue: true, axa: true },
  { feature: 'US Coverage', geoblue: 'Included (BCBS)', axa: 'Add-on' },
  { feature: 'Non-US Citizens', geoblue: 'Limited', axa: 'Yes' },
];

const pricingColumns = [
  { key: 'age', header: 'Age' },
  { key: 'geoblue', header: 'GeoBlue' },
  { key: 'axa', header: 'AXA Global' },
];

const pricingRows = [
  { age: '30', geoblue: '$150-230/mo', axa: '$140-220/mo' },
  { age: '40', geoblue: '$200-310/mo', axa: '$190-300/mo' },
  { age: '50', geoblue: '$280-430/mo', axa: '$260-400/mo' },
  { age: '60', geoblue: '$400-620/mo', axa: '$380-580/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="GeoBlue vs AXA Global"
  description="Compare GeoBlue and AXA Global health insurance. BCBS network for Americans vs European global coverage."
  headline="GeoBlue vs AXA Global"
  subheadline="US-focused BCBS affiliate vs European global insurer. Serving different expat populations."
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get Quotes from Both"
  ctaButtonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>
    GeoBlue and AXA Global serve different markets. GeoBlue is designed for US citizens with BCBS network access; AXA serves all nationalities with European-headquartered global coverage.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">GeoBlue</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>BCBS affiliated</li>
        <li>Designed for US citizens</li>
        <li>1.7M+ US providers</li>
        <li>US-based service</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">AXA Global</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Available to all nationalities</li>
        <li>French-headquartered</li>
        <li>Strong European networks</li>
        <li>Modular plan options</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Both Providers"
    description="Find the right fit for your nationality and needs."
    buttonText="Get Free Quotes"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="coverage-comparison">Coverage Comparison</h2>
  <p>
    Both offer comprehensive coverage, but target different populations. Eligibility is the first consideration.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={coverageColumns} rows={coverageRows} />
  </div>

  <p><strong>Key differences:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>GeoBlue is primarily for US citizens; AXA accepts all nationalities</li>
    <li>GeoBlue includes BCBS US network; AXA charges extra for US coverage</li>
    <li>GeoBlue has better mental health coverage</li>
    <li>AXA has stronger European hospital networks</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="pricing">Pricing</h2>
  <p>
    Pricing is similar when comparing apples to apples. AXA appears cheaper but excludes US coverage.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={pricingColumns} rows={pricingRows} />
  </div>

  <p><strong>Pricing notes:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>GeoBlue prices include BCBS US network access</li>
    <li>AXA prices exclude US; add 30-40% for inclusion</li>
    <li>For US citizens needing US coverage, GeoBlue is better value</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="network-and-claims">Network and Claims</h2>

  <h3>Provider Networks</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>GeoBlue</strong> provides access to 1.7+ million BCBS providers in the US—one of the largest networks available. International coverage is solid but US is the strength.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>AXA Global</strong> has extensive networks in Europe, Middle East, and Asia. US coverage is available but not as integrated as BCBS.
  </p>

  <h3>Service Approach</h3>
  <p>
    GeoBlue offers US-style customer service familiar to Americans. AXA's service follows European norms, which may feel different to US expats.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-should-choose">Who Should Choose Which</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose GeoBlue If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>You're a US citizen</li>
        <li>You want BCBS network access</li>
        <li>You visit the US regularly</li>
        <li>You prefer US-style service</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose AXA Global If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>You're not a US citizen</li>
        <li>You don't need US coverage</li>
        <li>You're based in Europe</li>
        <li>You want modular plan options</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="verdict">Our Verdict</h2>
  <p>
    The choice often comes down to citizenship. US citizens should seriously consider GeoBlue for the BCBS network access alone—it's hard to replicate that value elsewhere.
  </p>
  <p>
    Non-US citizens, or those who don't need US coverage, will find AXA Global offers excellent international coverage with the backing of a global insurance giant.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready to Decide?"
    description="Get quotes based on your situation."
    buttonText="Compare Plans Now"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> GeoBlue eligibility is primarily limited to US citizens. Verify eligibility and coverage with providers.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
